::Element/Prowl::

Element instantly lets go of Iron Raptor when he hears her words. His 
scanners had confirmed that both were Maximals, but he had tried to 
get them to stop fighting.

"I apologize," he says to Iron Raptor, dropping her back to the 
ground, "Did this bot attack you?"

A second after he asked his question, Element felt claws digging into 
his arm. Prowl had manage to turn himself around in the gestalt's 
grasp and scratch at Element's armor. Element growls, bringing his 
other hand back and slamming the back of his fist into Prowl's head. 
With a sickening, loud crunch originating from Prowl's head, his body 
goes limp, simply remaining still in Element's grasp.
